{"type":"text","timestamp":1781110484664,"sessionID":"ses_14d8b0795ffelFf5bOI1xNsAj3","part":{"id":"prt_eb2752c47001GF3ISpnGw4b3Ge","messageID":"msg_eb274fcd1001BKEcRJdH2GWuQ6","sessionID":"ses_14d8b0795ffelFf5bOI1xNsAj3","type":"text","text":"User specified the deep-review workflow and an explicit artifact root. I’ll load the workflow contract first, bind `artifact_dir` directly to the provided lineage path, then keep all review outputs inside that directory.","time":{"start":1781110484039,"end":1781110484663},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_090636393a4a31e8016a2996d3be4c81919e5972a77806d804","phase":"commentary"}}}}
