ine 18: | Track | Status | Leaf changelogs | Top rollup |\n\n  Line 20: | 000 release cleanup | planned | 0 | (scaffolded, not implemented) |\n\n  Line 31: | 011 command presentation workflow separation | planned | 0 | (scaffolded, not implemented) |\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/changelog/010-mcp-to-cli-tool-transition/changelog-010-mcp-to-cli-tool-transition-root.md:\n  Line 3: description: \"Complete rollup for the MCP-to-CLI tool transition phase: dual-stack CLI front-doors over all 3 MCP daemons (spec-memory 37 tools / code-index 8 tools / skill-advisor 9 tools), hardening suites, runtime hook integration, tri-daemon drill passed, and full doc-alignment sweep.\"\n\n  Line 25: | Phase | Title | Date | Status |\n\n  Line 27: | `001-spec-memory-cli` | spec-memory lane: research, core, hardening, runtime | 2026-06-06 to 2026-06-09 | Complete |\n\n  Line 28: | `001/000-spec-memory-cli-research` | Feasibility research (4 runs, GO verdict) | 2026-06-06 | Complete |\n\n  Line 29: | `001/001-cli-core` | CLI core: shim, IPC, 37 subcommands | 2026-06-07 | Complete |\n\n  Line 30: | `001/002-hardening-and-tests` | Hardening: dual-spawn, dual-client, lifecycle, parity | 2026-06-09 | Complete |\n\n  Line 31: | `001/003-runtime-integration` | Runtime: hooks, plugin bridge, allowlists | 2026-06-09 | Complete |\n\n  Line 32: | `002-code-index-cli` | code-index lane: research, core, hardening, runtime | 2026-06-06 to 2026-06-09 | Complete |\n\n  Line 33: | `002/000-code-index-cli-research` | Feasibility research (10 iterations, GO verdict) | 2026-06-06 | Complete |\n\n  Line 34: | `002/001-cli-core` | CLI core: manifest, shim, blocked-read | 2026-06-09 | Complete |\n\n  Line 35: | `002/002-hardening-and-tests` | Hardening: 6 suites, bridge repair | 2026-06-09 | Complete |\n\n  Line 36: | `002/003-runtime-integration` | Runtime: bridge repair, hooks, maintenance block | 2026