ability\n+- Novelty justification: No new findings; active P1 findings remain stable and require remediation.\n+\n+## Ruled Out\n+- P0 escalation remains rejected because the evidence shows recoverable metadata/resource-map drift, not data loss or security failure.\n+\n+## Dead Ends\n+- Additional iteration would likely restate the same parent drift without fixes.\n+\n+## Recommended Next Focus\n+Create a remediation plan to reconcile parent child inventory, resource-map coverage, and stale continuity/status prose.\n+Review verdict: PASS\n","additions":44,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-3/resource-map.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-3/resource-map.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-3/resource-map.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-3/resource-map.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-3/resource-map.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,11 @@\n+# Review Resource Map - fanout-gpt-3-1781110469935-pc6f9l\n+\n+## Phase-5 Augmentation\n+- Touched entries: `spec.md`, `description.json`, `graph-metadata.json`, `resource-map.md`, `timeline.md`, `changelog/README.md`, and `011-command-presentation-workflow-separation/spec.md`.\n+- Untouched entries: expected-by-scope entries include child implementation details below 011 and shipped phase leaves not needed to prove parent-control drift.\n+- Implementation paths absent from t